    "body": "Hi @kevinsawicki - very cool that this is an option. Unfortunately this isn't working:\r\n\r\n    browserWindow.loadURL('data:text/html,<script src=\"index.js\"></script>');\r\n\r\nThe script doesn't seem to be executing, although it does show up on the DOM.\r\n\r\nI tried this:\r\n\r\n    browserWindow.loadURL('data:text/html,<script src=\"file:///path/to/index.js\"></script>');\r\n\r\nBut got `Not allowed to load local resource`.\r\n\r\nWould love any insight you may have on this!"
